randomparas=["Every great achievement begins with a single step. Success does not come overnight, but through persistence, discipline, and the courage to face failure. Even the smallest progress matters, because each effort builds a stronger foundation for tomorrow. Technology has reshaped the way humans interact with the world. From the phone in your pocket to satellites orbiting Earth, everything is connected. While it makes life faster and more convenient, it also challenges us to balance efficiency with privacy and human connection."]